content.rendered:
EVOLUTION FRONT BAR SUITABLE FOR THE TOYOTA PRADO (pre-facelift)

The Evolution Bumper is finished in a hard-wearing Powder coat and available standard in black. It is a 3mm and 5mm steel construction and includes as standard a 5mm Aluminium bash plate not offered on other brands. The middle winch plate insert comes standard in black and can be optioned as stainless steel. We also ofer as standard, foglights which are an option on many other brands.

Includes:

Standard with Winch mount

Integrated imported Foglights

5mm Aluminium Bash / Protection plate

2 x Vehicle recovery points

Parking sensor and headlamp washer compatible – We can provide blanketing plugs for vehicles that don’t require sensors or washers.

Optional:

Can be colour coded to your vehicle specification

Middle winch plate insert can be optioned in stainless steel

Shackles

Winch

Spotlight bar

Spotlights
